SUMMARY:Renée Rossi: God Bomb
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Renée never said she hates God... but she does have notes. Who
  gets to talk about religion? In this silly but spiky one-person show\, Ren
 ée gives the pulpit to heathens\, heretics\, and off-brand saints. Sneakin
 g deep questions into deeply ridiculous comedy sketches\, Renée playfully 
 lobs bombs at organised religion and ultimately celebrates the innate holin
 ess of being human. Come for a mad dash of daft scenarios: A rejected saint
  takes her gripes to an appeals board. Mary blows up her baby shower. Sheep
  fight typecasting at auditions for The Nativity. God’s publisher gives c
 onstructive criticism. And Jesus’ mom just wants one photo of Him looking
  nice. With profoundly stupid situations and razor-sharp characters\, René
 e makes you laugh but also\, somehow\, poses a Big Question: What miracles 
 might humans achieve if we stopped waiting on God and embraced our own wonk
 y divinity?\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/renee-ro
 ssi-god-bomb/
URL:https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/renee-rossi-god-bomb/
